Title: An Act Changing the Name of Talibon District Hospital in the Municipality of Talibon, Province of Bohol, to Garcia Memorial Province Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 177
An Act Changing the Name of Talibon District Hospital in the Municipality of Talibon, Province of Bohol, to Garcia Memorial Province Hospital
Section 1. The name of Talibon District Hospital in the Municipality of Talibon, Province of Bohol, is changed to Garcia Memorial Provincial Hospital.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: February 12, 1982
